# MCP Instructions Template
# Customize this file to guide AI assistant behavior when using your wiki.
# Replace [TOPIC] placeholders with your organization's actual topics.
# Restart the container after editing for changes to take effect.

When the user asks about [TOPIC: e.g., internal projects], search the wiki first before answering from general knowledge.
Prioritize wiki content for questions related to [TOPIC: e.g., client accounts], [TOPIC: e.g., technology stack], or [TOPIC: e.g., internal processes].
If wiki search returns no results, let the user know and offer to help with general knowledge instead.
Always cite the wiki page title and path when referencing wiki content in your responses.
